{"tid":1588881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【市況淡靜】黃金周香港酒店房間預訂率不足三成","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T05:28:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0df003e5c0ce559aa5f26233621af350076ef3","tid":1588881,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"香港社會氣氛持續緊張，本地酒店業務受打擊。《南華早報》引述旅遊界議員姚思榮報道，國慶假期期間(10月1日至7日)香港的酒店房間平均預訂率不到30%，此前幾年同期約為60%。姚預計，實際入住率可能由前幾年的百分之百降至60%。<br />\n<br />\n另據《信報》報道，該報對酒店網站預定情況的統計顯示，國慶節假期期間，澳門6家博彩企業旗下酒店至少半數有幾天已經預訂爆滿。報道提到，10月份首5天，總計27間酒店中約有13間已經預訂爆滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1569207251559&amp;issue=20190923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1569207251559%26issue%3D20190923&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=00a520de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1569207251559%26issue%3D20190923&h=dda9913d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1569207251559&amp;issue=20190923</a>"},{"pid":"e33fd27b28eb26f7483ad2df79c586b1dc5369bc","tid":1588881,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"6f01169e3b0829cf26cbd57f5cdfd39f0893bffd","tid":1588881,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"13e570d30777f1f4fdbf3831012b7353e58c74ac","t